Boosterman

To view the code right click on boosterman.py and click edit.
It is better viewed in IDLE then other word processers.

To be able to run or edit the game you will need to download python 2.7.1 and pygame for windows

How to play:

Spacebar     : Jump

Left control : Jetpack

Left         : Left

Right	     : Right

Up           : UP

Down         : Down

Esc          : Quit



Hitting the spikeballs will kill you.
The spikes will spawn non stop until you either die or give up.
This game has no real objective yet but to dodge the spike balls.
